Description: We introduce a high-dimensional multi-study elliptical factor model (MultiEFM), 
    which learns latent features and accounts for the heterogeneity among sources. 
    It provides robust estimation for heterogeneous high-dimensional data analysis, 
    particularly suitable for multi-study RNA sequencing data and spatial multi-omics. 
    The package implements efficient algorithms for model configuration, identifiability 
    conditions, and parameter estimation.
